commit.message:
Fix architecture layer violations in core crate and API

- Remove escape_like() from dblentry-core (SQL-specific utility);
  add local copies in sqlite and postgres backends
- Remove prettytable-rs from dblentry-core; move DataValue Display
  impl to src/display.rs in main crate
- Add StorageError::DatabaseError variant for backend errors;
  sanitize messages in API mapper (returns generic 500, not raw SQL)
- Route /api/entities through proper handler functions;
  POST uses FQL execution via StatementExecutor

